Title: Minimax Estimation via Wavelet Shrinkage  a pleasure to acknowledge friendly conversations with Gerard Kerkyacharian,  
Author: David L. Donoho Iain M. Johnstone Catherine Laredo, and Dominique Picard. 
Keyword: Key Words. Minimax Decision theory. Minimax Bayes estimation. Besov, Holder, Sobolev, Triebel Spaces. Nonlinear Estimation. White Noise Model. Nonparametric regression. Orthonormal Bases of Compactly Supported Wavelets. Renormalization. White Noise Approximation.  
